## Styling Notes

- The design should be mobile-responsive
- Utilize the Bootstrap framework for components and grid layout
- The main font style for headings and text should be consistent with the brand

## Technical Specifications

- Ensure SEO-friendly markup and practices
- Prioritize performance and loading times
- Keep code easy to understand and maintain by following standard (see below)

## Standard & naming convention

- segment id: “S#”
  - e.g. S0, S1…
- segment code: “S#-<Segment short name>”
  - e.g S1-Quote
- css class names: “<segment code>-<class name>”
  - e.g S5-Donations-title
    – css segment start comment:
    /************************\*************************/
    /**\*\*\*** <segment code> styling - start **\*\***/
    /************************\*************************/
    – html segment start comment: <!--   <segment code> segment - start -->
    – html segment end comment: <!-- <segment code> segment - end -->

